snippet.title: Official Predecessor™: Closed Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Sign up for the Closed Alpha - https://omedastudios.com/alpha

Discord - https://discord.gg/Gww2FTf

Predecessor® is a fast-paced Third Person Action MOBA. Two teams consisting of heroes with unique designs and powerful abilities go head to head on the battlefield competing for the ultimate glory.
